reviews.review_text: The Day That Ricky Nelson Died ~ Tribute (??) The news broke just prior to this New Year's Eve Show, that Rick Nelson had just died in an airplane crash that day while on tour with his band.  My hunch is that is why the Grateful Dead spontaneously opened and then bookended the venue near 'Brokedown Palace' with Buddy Holly's 'Not Fade Away.'  As a reminiscent tribute to another Rock'n'Roll Legend who's career was abruptly ended midstream in a tragic plane accident.
